<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>WIA-RUST-LEARN - Zero-to-Rust</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --rust-orange: #f97316;
            --rust-dark: #c2410c;
            --bg: #0f172a;
            --bg-card: #1e293b;
            --bg-tertiary: #334155;
            --text: #f8fafc;
            --text-muted: #94a3b8;
            --border: #475569;
            --blue: #0EA5E9;
            --green: #10b981;
        }
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }

        /* Hero */
        .hero {
            padding: 80px 0;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg) 0%, #1a1a2e 100%);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        .hero-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--rust-orange);
            color: white;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--rust-orange), #fb923c);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .hero-philosophy {
            color: #fbbf24;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .hero-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .btn {
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--rust-orange);
            color: white;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--rust-dark); }
        .btn-secondary {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            color: var(--text);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--rust-orange); }

        /* Features */
        .features {
            padding: 80px 0;
        }
        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }
        .feature-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
        }
        .feature-card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .feature-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--rust-orange);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .feature-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: var(--rust-orange);
        }
        .feature-card p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        /* Curriculum */
        .curriculum {
            padding: 80px 0;
            background: var(--bg-card);
        }
        .level-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .level-card {
            background: var(--bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .level-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 4px;
            height: 100%;
            background: var(--rust-orange);
        }
        .level-num {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--rust-orange);
            opacity: 0.3;
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            right: 20px;
        }
        .level-card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .level-card .hours {
            color: var(--blue);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .level-card ul {
            list-style: none;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .level-card li {
            padding: 3px 0;
        }
        .level-card li::before {
            content: '→ ';
            color: var(--rust-orange);
        }

        /* Ownership Visual */
        .ownership {
            padding: 80px 0;
        }
        .ownership-demo {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 40px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .memory-viz {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 30px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .memory-section {
            background: var(--bg);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .memory-section h4 {
            color: var(--rust-orange);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .stack-item, .heap-item {
            background: var(--bg-tertiary);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 12px;
            margin: 8px 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .var-name { color: var(--blue); font-family: monospace; }
        .var-value { color: var(--green); font-family: monospace; }
        .ownership-legend {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .legend-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }
        .legend-color {
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        /* Certification */
        .certification {
            padding: 80px 0;
            background: var(--bg-card);
        }
        .cert-levels {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .cert-badge {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }
        .cert-badge:hover { transform: scale(1.1); }
        .cert-badge .icon { font-size: 2.5rem; }
        .cert-badge .name { font-weight: 600; margin-top: 5px; }
        .cert-bronze { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #cd7f32, #8b4513); }
        .cert-silver { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c0c0c0, #808080); }
        .cert-gold { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd700, #daa520); }
        .cert-platinum { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e5e4e2, #a9a9a9); }
        .cert-diamond { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b9f2ff, #4fc3f7); }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            padding: 40px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        footer .philosophy {
            color: #fbbf24;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        footer p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        footer a {
            color: var(--rust-orange);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
            .memory-viz { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <span class="hero-badge">WIA Standard</span>
            <h1>WIA-RUST-LEARN</h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">Zero-to-Rust: 중간 언어 없이, 처음부터 Rust로!</p>
            <p class="hero-philosophy">弘益人間 - 널리 인간을 이롭게 하라</p>
            <div class="hero-buttons">
                <a href="playground/" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">Try Playground</a>
                <a href="https://wiabooks.store/tag/wia-rust-learn-guide/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary">Read Ebook</a>
                <a href="https://wiabooks.store/tag/wia-rust-learn-guide-ko/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary">전자책 읽기</a>
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@yeonsamheum" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary" style="background: #FF0000; color: white; border: none;">📺 YouTube 28편</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features -->
    <section class="features">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Why WIA-RUST-LEARN?</h2>
            <div class="feature-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🎯</div>
                    <h3>Zero-to-Rust</h3>
                    <p>No intermediate languages. Start with Rust from day one. We believe Rust isn't hard - it's just different.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">👁️</div>
                    <h3>Visual Learning</h3>
                    <p>See memory in action. Our animated visualizations make ownership, borrowing, and lifetimes crystal clear.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🖥️</div>
                    <h3>Web Playground</h3>
                    <p>Monaco Editor with real-time compilation via WASM. Code, visualize, and learn in your browser.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">📚</div>
                    <h3>6-Level Curriculum</h3>
                    <p>Structured path from beginner to expert. Each level builds on the previous with hands-on projects.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🏆</div>
                    <h3>WIA Certification</h3>
                    <p>Earn Bronze to Diamond certifications. Prove your Rust skills with industry-recognized credentials.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🔗</div>
                    <h3>WIA Integration</h3>
                    <p>Build real projects with WIA standards. Connect with WIA-HOME, WIA-AI-CITY, and more.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Curriculum -->
    <section class="curriculum">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">6-Level Curriculum</h2>
            <div class="level-grid">
                <div class="level-card">
                    <span class="level-num">0</span>
                    <h3>Level 0: Setup</h3>
                    <div class="hours">2 hours</div>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Install Rust (rustup)</li>
                        <li>VS Code + rust-analyzer</li>
                        <li>Hello, World!</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="level-card">
                    <span class="level-num">1</span>
                    <h3>Level 1: Basics</h3>
                    <div class="hours">8 hours</div>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Variables & Types</li>
                        <li>Functions</li>
                        <li>Control Flow</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="level-card">
                    <span class="level-num">2</span>
                    <h3>Level 2: Ownership</h3>
                    <div class="hours">12 hours ⭐</div>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Stack vs Heap</li>
                        <li>Move, Copy, Clone</li>
                        <li>References & Borrowing</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="level-card">
                    <span class="level-num">3</span>
                    <h3>Level 3: Structure</h3>
                    <div class="hours">10 hours</div>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Structs & Enums</li>
                        <li>Pattern Matching</li>
                        <li>Modules</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="level-card">
                    <span class="level-num">4</span>
                    <h3>Level 4: Advanced</h3>
                    <div class="hours">12 hours</div>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Generics & Traits</li>
                        <li>Lifetimes</li>
                        <li>Smart Pointers</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="level-card">
                    <span class="level-num">5</span>
                    <h3>Level 5: Concurrency</h3>
                    <div class="hours">10 hours</div>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Threads</li>
                        <li>Message Passing</li>
                        <li>Mutex & Arc</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Ownership Visualization -->
    <section class="ownership">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">See Ownership in Action</h2>
            <div class="ownership-demo">
                <pre style="background: #1e1e1e; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; color: #d4d4d4; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; border-left: 4px solid var(--rust-orange);">
<span style="color: #569cd6;">fn</span> <span style="color: #dcdcaa;">main</span>() {
    <span style="color: #569cd6;">let</span> s1 = <span style="color: #4ec9b0;">String</span>::from(<span style="color: #ce9178;">"hello"</span>);
    <span style="color: #569cd6;">let</span> s2 = s1;  <span style="color: #6a9955;">// s1 moved to s2</span>
    <span style="color: #6a9955;">// println!("{}", s1); // Error: s1 no longer valid</span>
    <span style="color: #c586c0;">println!</span>(<span style="color: #ce9178;">"{}"</span>, s2);  <span style="color: #6a9955;">// OK: s2 owns the data</span>
}</pre>
                <div class="memory-viz">
                    <div class="memory-section">
                        <h4>Stack</h4>
                        <div class="stack-item" style="opacity: 0.4;">
                            <span class="var-name">s1</span>
                            <span class="var-value" style="color: #888;">moved →</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stack-item">
                            <span class="var-name">s2</span>
                            <span class="var-value">ptr, len, cap</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="memory-section">
                        <h4>Heap</h4>
                        <div class="heap-item">
                            <span class="var-name">[0x1234]</span>
                            <span class="var-value">"hello"</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="ownership-legend">
                    <div class="legend-item">
                        <div class="legend-color" style="background: #10b981;"></div>
                        <span>Owned</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="legend-item">
                        <div class="legend-color" style="background: #666;"></div>
                        <span>Moved</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="legend-item">
                        <div class="legend-color" style="background: #0EA5E9;"></div>
                        <span>Borrowed (&)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="legend-item">
                        <div class="legend-color" style="background: #eab308;"></div>
                        <span>Mut Borrowed (&mut)</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- YouTube Series -->
    <section class="youtube-series" style="padding: 80px 0; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #0f172a 100%);">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">📺 28편 YouTube 시리즈</h2>
            <p style="text-align: center; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 40px; font-size: 1.1rem;">
                교보문고 658페이지 책을 28편 영상으로! 움직이는 메모리 시각화로 배우는 Rust
            </p>
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 40px;">
                <div style="background: var(--bg-card); padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px; border-left: 4px solid #FF0000;">
                    <h3 style="color: var(--rust-orange); margin-bottom: 15px;">🎬 Level 0-5: Core (18편)</h3>
                    <ul style="color: var(--text-muted); list-style: none; line-height: 2;">
                        <li>• Level 0: 시작하기 (3편)</li>
                        <li>• Level 1: 기초 (4편)</li>
                        <li>• Level 2: 소유권 - NRT! (4편)</li>
                        <li>• Level 3: 구조화 (3편)</li>
                        <li>• Level 4: 고급 기능 (3편)</li>
                        <li>• Level 5: 동시성 (2편)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div style="background: var(--bg-card); padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px; border-left: 4px solid #8B5CF6;">
                    <h3 style="color: #8B5CF6; margin-bottom: 15px;">🔮 Level 6-8: Expert (6편)</h3>
                    <ul style="color: var(--text-muted); list-style: none; line-height: 2;">
                        <li>• Level 6: 테스팅 & 도구 (2편)</li>
                        <li>• Level 7: 고급 패턴 (2편)</li>
                        <li>• Level 8: Unsafe & 매크로 (2편)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div style="background: var(--bg-card); padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px; border-left: 4px solid #ffd700;">
                    <h3 style="color: #ffd700; margin-bottom: 15px;">👑 Level 9: Master (3편)</h3>
                    <ul style="color: var(--text-muted); list-style: none; line-height: 2;">
                        <li>• CLI Tool 프로젝트</li>
                        <li>• Web API (Axum)</li>
                        <li>• System Tool</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@yeonsamheum" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary" style="background: #FF0000; margin-right: 15px;">📺 YouTube 채널</a>
                <a href="WIA_RUST_LEARN_Colab.ipynb" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary">🎨 Colab으로 영상 만들기</a>
